caption.text:
6th of September...
What a really historical day for me. I always wanted to join the competition. I literally prepared everyday for it. And finally I was able to be a part of it.
But there was something I didn't realize at the time. The competition did not only test our intelligence, nor to get a necklace with round metal tied on it.
It's about the memories. It's about the new friends you made, from all over the city. It's about knowing the meaning of struggling, to achieve something you have been hoping and dreaming for years.
It's been 365 days and not even a single day passed without my flying thoughts about you guys. Hope to see you all again, together on the top...
